Distribution Restrictions
=========================

   IceBBS and its utility programs and documentation may not be
distributed by anyone without prior written consent of the Author,
Stephen Vermeulen.

   @{i}Only the demonstration version of IceBBS along with the
demonstration version of the documentation (in AmigaGuide or PostScript
format) may be freely distributed.@{ui}  The full version of IceBBS along
with the tools for FidoNet and USENET message processing and a printed
copy of this documentation are available from the Author for US$60.00,
plus $10.00 for shipping.


